—ЩParchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/hash_md5.mdЩ@27b94659958352224c8b95dc42f8d8d92775a6c03e4b082dde5a6d27c5917550Їtitle: hash md5‘ЁExamplesЪ2Return the md5 hash of a string, hex-encoded
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz' | hash md5
c3fcd3d76192e4007dfb496cca67e13b

```
Return the md5 hash of a string, as binary
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz' | hash md5 --binary
Length: 16 (0x10) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   c3 fc d3 d7  61 92 e4 00  7d fb 49 6c  ca 67 e1 3b   Г—Г—Г—Г—aГ—Г—0}Г—IlГ—gГ—;


```
Return the md5 hash of a file's contents
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> open ./nu_0_24_1_windows.zip | hash md5


```
